# ═══ API de Futebol — Copa / ao vivo ═══
# PRINCIPAL Copa 2026: worldcup26.ir (pública, sem chave, placar ao vivo)
# Docs: https://worldcup26.ir/api-docs
WORLDCUP26_API=1
# WORLDCUP26_API_URL=https://worldcup26.ir

# FALLBACK: football-data.org (10 req/min grátis)
# Cadastro: https://www.football-data.org/client/register
FOOTBALL_API_KEY=sua-chave-football-data

# OPCIONAL: API-Football — usada se worldcup26 falhar (100 req/dia grátis)
# Cadastro: https://www.api-football.com/ → dashboard → API Key
APISPORTS_KEY=sua-chave-api-football
